Fabric setup to manage a HBase cluster.

fabfile.py - fab file to drive Fabric.
region_mover.rb - JRuby script to manage HBase regions.
zkclient.py - ZooKeeper script to query/edit znode paths.

For more information on how these work with our setup - please take a
look at this post.

http://inchoate-clatter.blogspot.com/2012/03/hbase-ops-automation.html
